<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>

<body>
    <%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <h1>Who We Are</h1>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <main id="who-we-are">
        <!-- Our History Section -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Our History</h2>
            <p>Rwanda Blood Bridge was founded with the mission to ensure a safe and sufficient blood supply for
                patients in need. Over the years, we have grown into a trusted organization known for our dedication to
                saving lives through blood donation.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Values Section -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <div class="content-container">
                <img src="path/to/values.jpg" alt="Our Values" class="related-image">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p>We believe in the power of community, the importance of life-saving blood donations, and the
                        responsibility of ensuring that every drop of blood counts. We are driven by compassion,
                        integrity, and service to others.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Team Section -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
            <div class="content-container">
                <img src="path/to/team.jpg" alt="Our Team" class="related-image">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p>Our dedicated team of professionals works tirelessly to manage blood donations, coordinate with
                        hospitals, and engage with the community. Together, we strive to meet the needs of patients
                        across Rwanda.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Partners Section -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Our Partners</h2>
            <p>We collaborate with hospitals, government agencies, and non-profit organizations to ensure that our
                services reach those who need them the most. Together, we are building a stronger, healthier Rwanda.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>   

</body>

</html>